I prefer QxPf7+.  Black's choices are Kd8, in which case 12 Ne6+ picks off the black queen, or Kd6 which drives the black king into the battlefield.  Actually, Kd6 results with Ne4+ and again the black queen falls into darkness, trampled beneath the white knight's hooves.
